{
  "stem": "9899.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when we decided to go to Berlin and cross over the border, the Russian border, we were caught.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So that was another terrible moment for my mother, because she said, again, now the Russians will take us to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- at night, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this was at night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were trying-- my mother's friend, the three children, and my mother-- trying to cross over the railroad tracks, or the border, what it was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at that very moment, there was a group of Russians who had gone out, because they didn't care much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Russians were away from home, there was no more war, Berlin was half Russian anyway, so they were sitting there in their hut, just doing like this.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was not that difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But still, it was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because if they caught you, they would send you back to Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They also had camps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took us in, into their hut.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They caught us, and they took us in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the children, we were crying, scared, afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was besides myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't want to be caught.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't want to be shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because caught and shot and killed and blood was the same thing to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the German said, oh, don't worry, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he brought us chocolate, which we hadn't seen-- I had not known what chocolate was, because I couldn't remember from five years before.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he gave us hot milk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were very good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Russians, mean or bad or whatever their ideas are, they were very good to the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The children were never to be harmed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Through all their wars and through all their massacres, and through all their whatevers, children were always protected.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were the privileged of-- of the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
